reviewText: My son LOVES Tom and Jerry and he gets the biggest kick out of the movies. He watched it so many times that we had to get a new DVD.
Title: Tom and Jerry -  The Fast and the Furry

reviewText: My son and daughter both love this movie. Tom and Jerry will always be a classic franchise, but this is a really fun movie for kids, especially if they like cars.
Title: Tom and Jerry -  The Fast and the Furry

reviewText: Really good and enjoyable by kids cartoon. Like all of "Tom & Jerry", with bit of a violence. But it doesnt feel like real violence, because characters just keep going, even if they get hurt.
Title: Tom and Jerry -  The Fast and the Furry

reviewText: This movie is great my son loves this movie. Also you can't beat the price. I say the movie is a little over an hour and it is funny from what I hear.
summary: Good Movie For a Great price!
Title: Tom and Jerry -  The Fast and the Furry

reviewText: I like the old cartoons. no matter which cartoon it is, it seems as if the older ones are better made, better story etc
summary: Not a fan of new cartoons

reviewText: This wacky race kinda reminds me of wacky racers meets tom and jerry. It starts with tom and jerry fighting, spike too, tom and jerry get in a race thats suspose to go from hollywood to mexico. But with the different racers they end up going around the world! Its got tom and jerry antics, and just fully of laughs! Great family movie!
Title: Tom and Jerry -  The Fast and the Furry

reviewText: I got this for my 4 year old who loves Tom and Jerry.  I did not realize this was a full length movie.  I did not think my son would like it.  He has watched in several time and love it. A must have for the fan.
Title: Tom and Jerry -  The Fast and the Furry

reviewText: Hurray!!!  It's another Tom and Jerry Movie. This one has. become my grandsons Favorite.  It's about cross-country racing. Great Oldie!!!!!!
Title: Tom and Jerry -  The Fast and the Furry

reviewText: It was ok. There were too many lines in it that were obviouslly written for parents and they tried hard to be witty. Tom & j should be about physical comedy.
Title: Tom and Jerry -  The Fast and the Furry

reviewText: Its a good thing I enjoy watching T & J, cause we've watched this one 10 times ( it seems like more)! It keeps us occupied.
Title: Tom and Jerry -  The Fast and the Furry

reviewText: What can I say?  It's a perfect, good ol' classic, great for kids and adults alike!  You can't say that for many modern cartoons nowadays...
Title: Tom and Jerry -  The Fast and the Furry

reviewText: My grandkids all love the Tom and Jerry cartoons and movies.  They are action filled and show who is your true friend in the end!  I watched them and now my 3rd generation is watching them!
Title: Tom and Jerry -  The Fast and the Furry
